{"tid":1150613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丁權討論","createTime":"2019-05-12T03:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T05:45:23.000Z","uid":47058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"32abf51d45ef4e136e2f52dbba4feca8b25a7d5e","tid":1150613,"uid":47058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"[url<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fTf6T7mpCf4][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfTf6T7mpCf4%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=1a3f4124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fTf6T7mpCf4][/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係好識丁權既制度所以想請教同埋討論一下<br />\n<br />\n就丁權來講，如果話原意係要保障原居民有一個居住環境，點解唔係上面設限<br />\n<br />\n簡單所想設限有三種<br />\n<br />\n第一種係世襲制，即係套丁屋只能傳給下一代<br />\n<br />\n但甘就會有一個問題就係如果生多過一個丁就唔夠分，所以唔適用<br />\n<br />\n第二種係時限制，即係喺丁地使用權上設限<br />\n<br />\n簡單所想就係該名原居民同佢配偶在生期限作為土地使用期限，且不設繼期條款，甘既可以符合基本法中保障佢地既權益兼不影響其多於一名男丁，而且由於土地使用設限，套丁既意義減少<br />\n<br />\n第三當然就簡單於銷售上設限，但無甘做既原因係咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n當然我知我地點噏都未必有用，但集思廣益未必未來不能作參考<br />\n請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778941b30c5f818482b41ecba36e3977e7299843","tid":1150613,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"外來人口唔落閘<br />\n收曬丁地同太平洋都唔夠居住空間"},{"pid":"750be04f6b8e91bc1730e40d7c7432f4a3a0c7f9","tid":1150613,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬惡過狗"},{"pid":"3d6afcbd11323d5b89cbc337153075680c8df87a","tid":1150613,"uid":47058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"778941b30c5f818482b41ecba36e3977e7299843","tid":1150613,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"外來人口唔落閘<br />\n收曬丁地同太平洋都唔夠居住空間"},"cited